00:10:07.710 --> 00:10:09.520
Wow.

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:11.750
¿De verdad estoy bien?

00:10:13.270 --> 00:10:14.970
Es tan molesto.

00:10:14.970 --> 00:10:17.810
